body.message: When a photo is deleted from Unsplash, we will do everything we can to prevent its further distribution, including preventing it from being viewed and downloaded through Unsplash. However, the <link>Unsplash License</link> is irrevocable, so copies of the photo that were downloaded before deletion may still be used.
